      textEn: [
        "A group of vigorous young men. Behind them is a field of sorghum. They are as simple and honest as that sorghum.",
        "But look! Once the drumming starts, they go wild, ecstatic, frenzied! A hundred young men with drums slung diagonally across their backs, like a hundred stones hurled up by an earthquake, dance madly before you.",
        "What an Ansai Waist Drum!",
        "Yellow earth plateau, you gave birth to these spirited young men; only you can withstand such soul-shaking percussion!",
        "More intense! The body becomes heavy yet soaring thought!",
        "When it stopped abruptly, the world became strangely quiet, so unfamiliar. As if one had arrived on another planet. In the ear, a distant cock\u2019s crow."
      ],
